snippet.title: Field of the Dead Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Upcoming sci-fi horror story game by Mortality Core Games Inc.

Link to the indie game's website: https://www.fieldofthedead.com

Music is "Combat Theme #2" by Muz Station Productions in the Total Music Collection

The game will be released later this year
